comment: Regular Woodford, just in a limited edition Kentucky Derby label.
식도를 후드려 패는 느낌인데 살짝 부드러운 바닐라향이 기분좋았다
Regular woodford. Just in limited edition bottle.

I got one of these back in March impulsively and so glad I did because they sold out and I never saw again after that. Woodford is one of my favorites and I love the Kentucky Derby so I wanted the bottle!
